src:
ATEEZ's Hongjoong trends worldwide as fans celebrate his birthday
06 Nov 2019, 18:36 by sl278



ATEEZ's Hongjoong is trending worldwide as fans celebrate his birthday!



#홍중이가_가는곳이_원더랜드 (WhereverHongjoongGoesIsWonderland) and #Best_Leader_Hong_Day are trending 4 and 5 respectively as fans take over Twitter to wish the leader of ATEEZ a happy birthday!






Happy birthday, Hongjoong!
